Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE SACRED INHERITANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Head back to the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at ten hours.\NSadly, we have to head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Flora, let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee\Nwe'll find a way back in ten hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take our chances\Non finding Minakator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But then it'll take more time\Ngetting back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have two pieces of Kiseiseki,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but if we use Minakator,\Nit should repel the Malice of this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That should allow\NQueen Flora's Reremito to get us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it would take nothing\Nshort of a miracle to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're hoping to achieve\Nthe great miracle of defeating Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we hope to do that if we can't\Npull off a small miracle first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to fight them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right!\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was right in choosing you Leona.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your words have a power\Nthat gives people strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ten hours left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know we can obtain Minakator!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've learned to\Nrapid-fire the Arrow Type!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think this is enough\Nto counter Ban's Kaiser Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I pierced his spell before,\NI used the Break Type.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I don't have my sword and\NI can't use attacks with my Dragonic Aura,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I need an attack as fast as the Arrow Type\Nand as powerful as the Break Type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nova, could you ready yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought up a new attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A new attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you discovered\Na third type of Aban Strash?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing that impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Have your Aura Blade at full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks like the same stance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If my weapon wasn't an Aura Blade\Nthat would've taken my head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a small part of our arsenal,\Nbut we've got a new power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"A small part"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, it looks like you've created\Na terrifying new attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You never cease to amaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I tried to rival you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And my timing is still off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's keep training!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the 25th level.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The level where Minakator can be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense a strange power\Nfrom the center area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the ritual altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So I pray here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wear your Insignia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:08:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the monsters to us.\NFocus on the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a welcoming party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do so many monsters inhabit\Na cave made by the God of Humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,According to ancient texts of a Sage,\Nthe lowest level of the Cave of Trials
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,connects to the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ritual of Inheritance is beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,God of Humans,\Ngrant me this legendary spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The word of strength\Nimbued with holy power...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Minakator!{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not real fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's spiritual energy.\NA flame of the soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's an illusion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This must be a test\Nleft by the God of Humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If Leona is unworthy of using Minakator...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe this flame will incinerate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, be strong! Maintain a strong will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.56,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEHOMA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NHEAL-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:36.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}REFRACTOR FIST{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You who seek Minakator, present your soul.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My... soul?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reveal the root of your soul\Nwhich seeks the power of purification.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you a purpose\Nworthy of this great power or not?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't answer\Nsuch a difficult question so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have one reason\Nfor seeking the power of purification!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In the world I was born and raised in!\NIn all its countries!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And in all the people who live there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not to defeat evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to prove that the things\Nwe've inherited weren't in the wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, I need power! That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that white light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the will to see the truth\Nand pursue what is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That is Leona's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of the soul of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Minakator!{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A pillar of light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Betan!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much\NI expend my Magic Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I punish myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,glow at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, even though\Nhis was provisional, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's father was a Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona's the Princess of Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam's parents were the Warrior\Nand Cleric from Master Aban's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel's a combat pro who's been trained\Nby both good and evil since he was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who's different!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Popp? Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You came here looking for advice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be my mentor, but this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I give advice\Nwhen you won't say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a Seer, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that asking for advice from you\Nwon't solve what's troubling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my own problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Though...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it's something\NI can do anything about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just the normal son of\Na weapons merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I've finally hit\Na wall I can't overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But... even so!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be\Na burden on everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I should do anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm actually kind of flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Flattered?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But seeing the green little brat\NI trained finally reach this level
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,makes me both happy and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel all tingly inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I never had a wife or a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess this is what\Nbeing a parent would feel like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've taught you Medoroa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes to combat,\Nyou've probably surpassed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had an Insignia of Matorif,\NI'd have given it to you a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mentor, for whining like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... I'll figure it out for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up. This is\Nthe last piece of advice I have for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The last"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Believe in myself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were just a spoiled brat,\Nyou never would have come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were a weak son of\Na weapons merchant, you looked up to Aban,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and struggled harder than anyone\Nto make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud to call you my student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp, I'm pretty sure I know\Nwhat you're going through.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will probably be\Nthe biggest hurdle of your life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if you can overcome it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you'll make it to a place\Nthat I never could.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have attained\Nthe Great Purification Spell, Minakator!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall succeed in our plan\Nto rescue Hyunckel and Crocodine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and then send the Hero's party\Ninto Ban Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Princess made it back safely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It was pretty easy, right everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That Kiseiseki should glow for you\Nas an Insignia of Aban now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. Leona's a royal princess\Nand even she's trying hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to try at least ten times harder!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you? Did your training go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Go well? He easily invented a new attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I just need a sword\Nthat can endure my Dragonic Aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we had your Sword of Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Flora! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A Darkling is approaching the Fort!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! He's not an enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What a hostile welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed! You're insulting your savior here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on! Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Princess!\NIt's good to see you're well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark King used the staff, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The Kōmanotue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really make it, Ron Berku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I did. With that in hand,\NBan is truly unbeatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Face to face, you don't\Nstand a chance against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you even find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Is that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This came to me along with\NHyunckel's Dark Armour Spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These weapons came to me seeking\Ngreater power for the battle ahead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I accepted their plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the newly reborn Sword of Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,May I draw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The feel of it in my hand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've missed this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself to me, my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:12.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:18.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:24.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:29.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:35.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:41.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:47.55,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:53.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:59.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:05.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:10.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:16.83,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:22.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:30.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As Dai invents a new attack,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ron Berku arrives, bringing the restored\NSword of Dai and other new weapons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morale is high, but Maam and Amy\Nare not their usual selves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Popp still struggles\Nto make his Insignia of Aban glow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the battle approaches,\Nthings grow strained.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:23:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.17,0:23:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Night Before the Battle"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:24:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.04,On Top,,0,0,0,,
